HDBUr 'aShUr HYH 'aL-YUrMYHV M'aTh YHVH L'aMUr.
ShM'yV 'aTh-DBUrY HBUrYTh HZ'aTh VDBUrThM 'aL-'aYSh YHVDH V'yL-YShBY YUrVShLM.
V'aMUrTh 'aLYHM KH-'aMUr YHVH 'aLHY YShUr'aL 'aUrVUr H'aYSh 'aShUr L'a YShM'y 'aTh- DBUrY HBUrYTh HZ'aTh.
'aShUr TShVYThY 'aTh-'aBVThYKM BYVM HVTShY'aY-'aVThM M'aUrTSh-MTShUrYM MKVUr HBUrZL L'aMUr ShM'yV BQVLY V'yShYThM 'aVThM KKL 'aShUr-'aTShVH 'aThKM VHYYThM LY L'yM V'aNKY 'aHYH LKM L'aLHYM.
LM'yN HQYM 'aTh-HShBV'yH 'aShUr-NShB'yThY L'aBVThYKM LThTh LHM 'aUrTSh ZBTh ChLB VDBSh KYVM HZH V'a'yN V'aMUr 'aMN YHVH.
VY'aMUr YHVH 'aLY QUr'a 'aTh-KL-HDBUrYM H'aLH B'yUrY YHVDH VBChTShVTh YUrVShLM L'aMUr ShM'yV 'aTh-DBUrY HBUrYTh HZ'aTh V'yShYThM 'aVThM.
KY H'yD H'yDThY B'aBVThYKM BYVM H'yLVThY 'aVThM M'aUrTSh MTShUrYM V'yD-HYVM HZH HShKM VH'yD L'aMUr ShM'yV BQVLY.
