VY'aMUr YHVH 'aLY NMTSh'a-QShUr B'aYSh YHVDH VBYShBY YUrVShLM.
ShBV 'yL-'yVNTh 'aBVThM HUr'aShNYM 'aShUr M'aNV LShMV'y 'aTh-DBUrY VHMH HLKV 'aChUrY 'aLHYM 'aChUrYM L'yBDM HPhUrV BYTh-YShUr'aL VBYTh YHVDH 'aTh-BUrYThY 'aShUr KUrThY 'aTh-'aBVThM.
LKN KH 'aMUr YHVH HNNY MBY'a 'aLYHM Ur'yH 'aShUr L'a-YVKLV LTSh'aTh MMNH VZ'yQV 'aLY VL'a 'aShM'y 'aLYHM.
VHLKV 'yUrY YHVDH VYShBY YUrVShLM VZ'yQV 'aL-H'aLHYM 'aShUr HM MQTUrYM LHM VHVSh'y L'a-YVShY'yV LHM B'yTh Ur'yThM.
KY MSPhUr 'yUrYK HYV 'aLHYK YHVDH VMSPhUr ChTShVTh YUrVShLM ShMThM MZBChVTh LBShTh MZBChVTh LQTUr LB'yL.
V'aThH 'aL-ThThPhLL B'yD-H'yM HZH V'aL-ThSh'a B'yDM UrNH VThPhLH KY 'aYNNY ShM'y B'yTh QUr'aM 'aLY B'yD Ur'yThM.
