V'aNY KKBSh 'aLVPh YVBL LTBVCh VL'a-YD'yThY KY-'yLY ChShBV MChShBVTh NShChYThH 'yTSh BLChMV VNKUrThNV M'aUrTSh ChYYM VShMV L'a-YZKUr 'yVD.
